726470f.title: Queens: Denman Street - Elmhurst Avenue
726470f.text:
Denman Street (foreground), south side, east of Elmhurst Ave.,
showing at the right foreground the A. Gorstine farmhouse from 1852-
1860 1 - to his estate from 1873 to 1891. It was the property of the
American Democratic Club in 1924.
March 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

726531f-b.title: Queens: Elmhurst Avenue - Denman Street.
726531f-b.text:
Elmhurst Avenue, east side, between Denman and Elbertson
Streets, showing several old dwellings, the center one of
which is the A. Gorsline house. It appears on J. Riker Jr's
1852 Map of Newtown. It later becamme the Amerind Democratic

726532f-a.title: Queens: Elmhurst Avenue - Denman Street
726532f-a.text:

has been developed within the last ten years.
